---
const today = new Date();
const baseURL = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<footer class="site-footer">
	<div class="shell footer-shell">
		<div class="footer-copy">
			<p class="eyebrow">sonder</p>
			<h2>保持热爱，无限进步。</h2>
			<p>这里记录我在编程学习路上的理解变化、实践过程，以及那些值得慢下来回看的成长片段。</p>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-meta">
			<div class="footer-links">
				<a href={baseURL}>首页</a>
				<a href={`${baseURL}blog`}>全部文章</a>
				<a href={`${baseURL}about`}>关于我</a>
			</div>
			<a class="mail" href="mailto:3192422357@qq.com">3192422357@qq.com</a>
			<p class="copyright">© {today.getFullYear()} sonder</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<style>
	.site-footer {
		padding-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.footer-shell {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(280px, 0.8fr);
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 252, 247, 0.76), rgba(255, 248, 239, 0.88));
		border: 1px solid rgba(114, 138, 123, 0.14);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	.footer-copy {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.9rem;
	}

	.footer-copy h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem);
	}

	.footer-meta {
		display: grid;
		align-content: space-between;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.footer-links {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.footer-links a,
	.mail {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: fit-content;
		padding: 0.7rem 0.95rem;
		border-radius: 999px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(114, 138, 123, 0.16);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		color: var(--ink-soft);
	}

	.footer-links a:hover,
	.mail:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		background: white;
		color: var(--ink);
	}

	.copyright {
		font-size: 0.92rem;
		color: var(--ink-faint);
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.footer-shell {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			padding: 1.4rem;
		}
	}
</style>
